# secrets — never commit; the app doesn't use .env at runtime (keys live encrypted in
# ~/Library/Application Support/notely, entered via the in-app Settings UI), but this
# stays defensive in case one's ever added for local scripting/dev convenience
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

